"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348150","Department of Health","false","2015-06-10","<p>NHS England has advised that there are minutes for all the meetings of the Specialised Commissioning Oversight Group. The minutes of this meeting are currently not published. But, in the context of NHS England’s endeavours to improve transparency and access to documents which include key decisions of public interest they will be reviewing this position.</p><p> </p>","Mid Norfolk","George Freeman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348150/answer",,,,,,"2015-06-10T16:21:52.243Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348150/answer","Biography information for George Freeman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348150/answer",,,,,,,,"17","Health","Health","2015-06-02","Specialised Commissioning Oversight Group: Meetings","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, whether minutes exist for each meeting of the Specialised Commissioning Oversight Group undertaken to date; if he will publish the agendas for and minutes of each such meeting; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","910"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348151","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2015-06-10","<p /> <p>The Department for Work and Pensions does not collect information on the EU citizenship status of claimants for Disability Living Allowance and Personal Independence Payment.</p>","North Swindon","Justin Tomlinson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348151/answer",,,,,"947","2015-06-10T11:02:40.127Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348151/answer","Biography information for Justin Tomlinson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348151/answer",,,,,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2015-06-02","Social Security Benefits: Parkinson's Disease","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, how many citizens of other EU member states with Parkinson's disease receive disability living allowance or personal independence payments.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","911"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348152","Department of Health","false","2015-06-10","<p>A list of the names and positions of the members of NHS England's Clinical Priorities Advisory Group and NHS England's Specialised Commissioning Oversight Group are attached.</p><p> </p>","Mid Norfolk","George Freeman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348152/answer","CPAG membership.docx","CPAG membership.docx","NHS England's CPAG & SCOG membership ","NHS England's CPAG & SCOG membership ","913","2015-06-10T16:46:53.457Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348152/answer","Biography information for George Freeman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/348152/answer",,,,,,,,"17","Health","Health","2015-06-02","Clinical Priorities Advisory Group: Membership","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what the names and positions are of the members of NHS England's Clinical Priorities Advisory Group.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","912"
